Oh and about paganism, guys. I would like to shed some light on the situation, being a former wiccan for a time.
Wicca celebrates the worship of the earth, as our ancestors did long ago, and actual pagans and wiccans dont mesh up the trinity of the worst religions on the planet, christios judeos and islamabaz, into a big stew pot. Those kinds of people are not pagans, and should be ignored. And wiccans are not as stupid as they are depicted as, plus they are persecuted far more than we are
I just wish people would cut the world's most tolerant and peaceful religion some slack
